  "title": "NgPlural",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_plural.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L14-L81\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_plural.ts#L14-L81\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/NgPlural\", \"name\": \"NgPlural\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"ngplural\">NgPlural<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#ngplural\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label experimental\">experimental</label>\n    \n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Adds / removes DOM sub-trees based on a numeric value. Tailored for pluralization.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"directive-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({ selector: '[<a href=\"api/common/NgPlural\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPlural</a>]' })\nclass <a href=\"api/common/NgPlural\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgPlural</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#constructor()\">constructor(_localization: NgLocalization)</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#ngPlural\">set ngPlural: number</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#addCase\">addCase(value: string, switchView: SwitchView): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"selectors\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">Selectors<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading selector\">\n  [<a href=\"api/common/NgPlural\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPlural</a>]\n  </code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"inputs\">\n  <h2 id=\"inputs\">Inputs<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#inputs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <div class=\"input\">\n    <code><a href=\"api/common/NgPlural\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPlural</a></code> bound to <code><a href=\"api/common/NgPlural#ngPlural\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgPlural.ngPlural</a></code>\n    \n  </div>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">Displays DOM sub-trees that match the switch expression value, or failing that, DOM sub-trees\nthat match the switch expression's pluralization category.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">To use this directive you must provide a container element that sets the <code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgPlural\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPlural</a>]</code> attribute\nto a switch expression. Inner elements with a <code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgPluralCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPluralCase</a>]</code> will display based on their\nexpression:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>if <code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgPluralCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPluralCase</a>]</code> is set to a value starting with <code>=</code>, it will only display if the value\nmatches the switch expression exactly,</li>\n<li>otherwise, the view will be treated as a \"category match\", and will only display if exact\nvalue matches aren't found and the value maps to its category for the defined locale.</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">See <a href=\"http://cldr.unicode.org/index/cldr-spec/plural-rules\">http://cldr.unicode.org/index/cldr-spec/plural-rules</a></p>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  <h2 id=\"constructor\">Constructor<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#constructor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <a id=\"constructor()\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table constructor\">\n  \n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">constructor(_localization: <a href=\"api/common/NgLocalization\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgLocalization</a>)</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table constructor-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"constructor-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>_localization</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code><a href=\"api/common/NgLocalization\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgLocalization</a></code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"properties\">Properties<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table properties-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"ngPlural\"></a>ngPlural</td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code>number</code></label></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"methods\">Methods<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#methods\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"addCase\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th><h3 id=\"addcase\">\n    addCase()\n    \n  <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#addcase\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3></th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">addCase(value: string, switchView: SwitchView): void</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters-1\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>value</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>string</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>switchView</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>SwitchView</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>void</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage Notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgPlural#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example>\n&#x3C;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgPlural\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPlural</a>]=\"value\">\n  &#x3C;ng-template <a href=\"api/common/NgPluralCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPluralCase</a>=\"=0\">there is nothing&#x3C;/ng-template>\n  &#x3C;ng-template <a href=\"api/common/NgPluralCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPluralCase</a>=\"=1\">there is one&#x3C;/ng-template>\n  &#x3C;ng-template <a href=\"api/common/NgPluralCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngPluralCase</a>=\"few\">there are <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> few&#x3C;/ng-template>\n&#x3C;/some-element>\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgPluralCase\n - api/common/getLocalePluralCase\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgLocalization\n - api/common/NgPlural#addCase\n - api/common/NgPlural#addcase\n - api/common/NgPlural#constructor\n - api/common/NgPlural#constructor()\n - api/common/NgPlural#description\n - api/common/NgPlural#inputs\n - api/common/NgPlural#methods\n - api/common/NgPlural#ngPlural\n - api/common/NgPlural#ngplural\n - api/common/NgPlural#properties\n - api/common/NgPlural#selectors\n - api/common/NgPlural#usage-notes\n - api/common/NgPluralCase\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - http://cldr.unicode.org/index/cldr-spec/plural-rules\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_plural.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L14-L81\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_plural.ts#L14-L81\n-->"
